            </div>
            <p class="testimonial-text">"The rewards system is amazing. I earn points on every purchase and can use them anywhere Tap2 is accepted. It's basically free money!"</p>
            <div class="testimonial-author">
              <div class="author-avatar">EP</div>
              <div class="author-info">
